Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:11.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游魂  ～Pure my heart～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是个好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫  猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且像大清早就猫在起居室里爸爸一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.75,0:00:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  早上好  天气真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会说话!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要来一杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会喝咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.96,0:00:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要来片烤面包？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这状态是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗  是梦吗  是什么的预兆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.48,0:00:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.54,0:00:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:01:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是亚兹拉尔而已  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚兹拉尔先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我亚兹就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会抽雪茄？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚兹先生在这里做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.58,0:01:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无所作为的话又会转瞬而逝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.46,0:01:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候才后悔就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片烤面包也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然热着的时候很好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面在说什么根本听不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  现在能做掉的事情就绝不要拖到后面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.09,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁年轻  多辛苦辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说还太难了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总有一天  你一定会能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.07,0:02:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊  我们今天都多加把油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回自己家咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.73,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天也要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（捡走我吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对啊…
